Transform a table to a gt object

Source: R/query_panda.R
bio_tab_to_gt.Rd

A short description...

Usage

bio_tab_to_gt(tab_for_gt)

Arguments

tab_for_gt

A data.table or a list of data.tables.

Value

A gt::gt table. If tab_for_gt is a list, the names of the list are used as grouping variable for table.
